===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=dú wàn juàn shū, xíng wàn lĭ lù|pint=du2wan4juan4shu1xing2wan4li3lu4|tra=讀萬卷書，行萬里路|sim=读万卷书，行万里路|rs=讠08}}
# There's more to life than book smarts, there's street smarts as well; In order attain wisdom, it is not enough merely to read books, you must be well travelled as well.

